articles.title: Novo Nordisk's Wegovy weight loss drug launches in the UK - CNBC
articles.description: Novo Nordisk launched its Wegovy weight loss injection in the U.K. Monday, furthering the drug's rollout in Europe despite ongoing supply constraints.
articles.content:
Novo Nordisk launched its Wegovy weight loss injection in the U.K. on Monday, advancing the drug's rollout in Europe despite ongoing supply constraints.
